data.description: Discover a Toll Brothers Ridgewood model,  in Lusitano Ranch, a small gated community of luxury single story homes. This modern farmhouse offers 5 bedrooms with designer walk in closets, 5 bathrooms, and a 4-car garage on a spacious 21,344 sqft lot. The backyard is a blank canvas, ready for your creative touch. Inside, indulge your culinary desires in the gourmet kitchen with sub zero fridge, and top-of-the-line appliances with a generous center island. This exclusive community provides privacy and peaceful surroundings. Don't miss the opportunity to own this Toll Brothers masterpiece.
